---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Section, SubSection, SubSectionHeader, Icon, Navigation, Footer, PageTitle } from '../../components';
---

<Layout title="Diploi - AI Job roles available" description='Learn about our AI job role.'>
  <Navigation selected="jobs" />
  <main>
    <Section isNarrow>
      <PageTitle tagText="Jobs" title="Full-stack developer with interest in AI" />
      <SubSection>
        <SubSectionHeader title="TL;DR" />
        <p>
          We are looking for a full-stack developer with a keen interest in working with AI solutions.
          <br />
          If you think you are able to develop features that change the future of software engineering this position is for you.
        </p>
      </SubSection>
      <SubSection>
        <SubSectionHeader title="Who We Are" icon="HandWaving" />
        <p>
          Diploi is redefining cloud development with a <b>simple</b>, <b>scalable</b>, and <b>powerful</b> PaaS solution. Our goal is to provide
          a Developer Experience that looks and feels just <span class="text-gradient">magical</span>.
          <br /><br />
          We are still very early on so joining now will enable you to make a real impact on the product as well as being one of the first employees.
        </p>
      </SubSection>
      <SubSection>
        <SubSectionHeader title="Who We're Looking For" icon="MagnifyingGlass" />
        <p>We are hiring Software Developers who obsess with</p>
        <ul class="checks">
          <li>
            <Icon isGradient name="CheckSquare" weight="regular" /> Developer Experience
          </li>
          <li>
            <Icon isGradient name="CheckSquare" weight="regular" /> Artificial Intelligence
          </li>
          <li>
            <Icon isGradient name="CheckSquare" weight="regular" /> Scalability &amp; Performance
          </li>
          <li>
            <Icon isGradient name="CheckSquare" weight="regular" /> Working on hard tasks and having a good time
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          You don't need to check every box, but if you're curious, driven and love solving hard problems, we'd love to hear from you!
          <br /><br />
          Our offices are in Helsinki, Finland and we work on-site once per week. We would prefer if you can do that also.
        </p>
        <p>
          <b>Our Tech Stack</b>
          <br /><br />
          Frontend: React for user interfaces
          <br />
          Backend: Typescript, PostgreSQL, Kubernetes
          <br />
          Cloud: Cloudflare, AWS, Terraform
        </p>
      </SubSection>
      <SubSection>
        <article class="card large">
          <div class="title-and-description">
            <h2>
              <Icon isGradient name="EnvelopeOpen" isGradient sizeRem={3} /> How to apply
            </h2>
            <p>
              Email us at
              <a href="mailto:hiring@diploi.com">hiring@diploi.com</a>
              with
            </p>
            <ul class="checks">
              <li>
                <Icon name="ArrowRight" weight="regular" /> Your resume / LinkedIn / GitHub
              </li>
              <li>
                <Icon name="ArrowRight" weight="regular" /> A short intro about why you're interested
              </li>
              <li>
                <Icon name="ArrowRight" weight="regular" /> Any projects or code you're proud of
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              Come and create <span class="text-gradient">magic</span> with us!
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </SubSection>
    </Section>
  </main>
</Layout>
<Footer />

<style lang="scss">
  @use '../../styles/mixins';

  p {
    max-width: unset;
  }

  .title {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-huge);

    .title-and-description {
      @include mixins.sparkle-bg;
    }
  }

  .checks {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;

    > li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--space-l);
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }

  .positions {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;

    > li {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      background: transparent;
      padding: 0;
      padding: var(--space-xxl) 0;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;

      :global(.job-position-icon) {
        @include mixins.card-bg-icon;
        @include mixins.respond-to('tablet') {
          left: unset;
          right: 0;
          width: 8rem !important;
          height: 8rem !important;
          top: 50%;
          transform: translate(0%, -50%);
        }
      }

      > svg {
        margin-bottom: var(--space-m);
        opacity: 0.5;
      }

      > h3 {
        font-size: 24px;
      }

      > h3,
      p {
        margin: 0;
      }
    }
  }

  .card {
    @include mixins.card-desktop;
    @include mixins.sparkle-bg(2);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xxl);

    @include mixins.respond-to('tablet') {
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    h2 {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--space-l);
    }
  }
</style>
